AB  - Against the backdrop of the logistics industry's acceleration toward digital transformation, the impact of digital logistics on supply chain efficiency is analyzed in this study using panel data from 2014 to 2023 of 30 Chinese provinces. The results of robustness tests indicate that digital logistics significantly enhances supply chain efficiency, with supply chain finance playing a significant mediating role by alleviating corporate financing constraints. Supply chain efficiency through digital logistics varies across regions, showing significant improvements in the eastern and central regions, but none in the western region.
